TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed FtpStatusCode extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: Specifies the status codes returned for a File Transfer Protocol (FTP) operation.

remarks.format:
## Remarks The <xref:System.Net.FtpStatusCode> enumeration defines the values returned in the <xref:System.Net.FtpWebResponse.StatusCode%2A> property.
For additional information about FTP server status codes, see [RFC 959: "File Transfer Protocol", Section 4.2: "FTP Replies"](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc959.txt).
## Examples The following code example sends an FTP request to make a new directory on an FTP server and checks the status code returned in the response.
[!code-cpp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/cpp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CPP/ftptests.cpp#22)] [!code-csharp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CS/ftptests.cs#22)]
